> Cheetara:So panthos can i help?I like to destroy things.

{Panthos}

    The panther bot continues north, his paws making very little noise
amongst the brush as he moves ignoring the queries of Cheetara, his eyes
instead focusing on the looming ruins of Maximal City ahead. He'd soon be
within Comm range as well as scanning range, likely they'd have detected his
signature by now...He wasn't worried, his "disguise" had fooled the bot back
at the Catz base, it shouldn't fail here. At least he hoped it didn't. He
wasn't in much shape to try dodging a second bases defenses all in the one
afternoon....
